		<title>SHA-1 vulnerable : consider SHA-2</title>
		<link>/blog-archive/2009/05/10/sha-1-vulnerable-consider-sha-2.html</link>
		<pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2009 07:58:50 +0000</pubDate>
